Class TileEntity

    • net.minecraft.tileentity.TileEntity

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TileEntityTickable

    public class TileEntity
extends net.minecraft.tileentity.TileEntity
    TileEntity is an internal class that should only be extended when you need to implement an interface. If you need to create a standard tile entity and wound up here, take a look at BlockEntity instead.
